quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Ha, Mim."
  44,2,"Nditsuba khushitabu shinoosinjia."
  44,3,"Toto efwe khwashishia mushilo shietsikhabi, toto efwe khuli abekanyilisi."
  44,4,"Toto eshilo esho buli likhuwa eliamachesi linoosibungwa."
  44,5,"Likhuwa lirula khwifwe, toto efwe nefwe Abaruma."
  44,6,"Tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto Ye ni Omuwulili po, Omumanyi muno."
  44,7,"Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, nende bioosi bili hakari wabio, toto nimuli mbu mwasuubila noobwatoto."
  44,8,"Abulaho Nyasaye wundi halali Ye tawe, alamusinjia ne afwisinjia. Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi khandi owabasenywe beyimbeli."
  44,9,"Halali bo bali mutsinganakani, babayanga sa."
  44,10,"Kho linda inyanga yelikulu liakharusie omwosi kulolekha."
  44,11,"Kulifunikha Abandu, shino ni eshinyasio eshilulu."
  44,12,""Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khuyiniliekhwo eshinyasio, toto efwe khulasuubila.""
  44,13,"Okhwitsulila khwabu khubakhoonya shina bulano, ne toto Omurumwa Omwinoosia yamala okhubeetsela."
  44,14,"Mana nibamuhelesia omukongo, nibaboola mbu: “Uno yechesibwa, naye ni Omulalu.”"
  44,15,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhuyiniaho eshinyasio hatiti, ne toto enywe mulakalukha shinga mwali."
  44,16,"Inyanga yakhulikhupa eshikhupo eshikhongo, toto efwe khulibarunga imongo."
  44,17,"Ne toto efwe khwakholela Abandu ba Firauni amatemo imbeli wabu, ne yaboolela Omurumwa woluyali."
  44,18,"Naboola mbu: “Mumbe (akeekhoyeshele), Abasumba ba Nyasaye, toto esie endi Omurumwa omwisikwa khwinywe."